授、蝴蝶研究领域权威榊史朗承认自己杀害他们并将其制成“人类标本”，主动自首。他执念于“让美永恒存在”的疯狂信念，最终连挚爱的儿子也被卷入疯狂之中。", "rating": {"count": 1126, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.0, "value": 6.0}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2927024179.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2927024179.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37316476", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928451255.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928451253.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928451264.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928451263.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2025", "card_subtitle": "2025 / 日本 / 剧情 惊悚 / 广木隆一 / 西岛秀俊 市川染五郎", "title": "人类标本", "type": "tv", "id": "37316476", "tags": []}, {"comment": "“即使是法官，也只是人。”他们身处审判他人的位置，却并不总能作出绝对正确的判断。年轻法官安堂清春（任职第七年）被派往本州最西端的Y地方法院，面对复杂的案件与人性困境：在庭审中突然翻供的黑社会成员、面带微笑承认弑夫的女教师、坚称女儿被人杀害的父亲……每一个案件都让他在正义与良知之间挣扎。自幼被诊断为发育障碍的他，也必须直面自我与脆弱的内心。这是一部描绘年轻法官在“裁与被裁”之间摸索成长的青春法庭悬疑剧。\n本剧改编自直岛翔的同名原著小说。", "rating": {"count": 213, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.5, "value": 7.1}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2927600450.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2927600450.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37659228", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929366387.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929366386.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928775276.jpg", "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2928775273.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2026", "card_subtitle": "2026 / 日本 / 剧情 / 吉川久岳 山下和德 相良健一 富澤昭文 / 松山研一 鸣海唯", "title": "忒弥斯的不确定法庭", "type": "tv", "id": "37659228", "tags": []}, {"comment": "该剧以圣诞节为背景，描绘围绕谎言展开的人间百态。主人公大森光（菊地凛子 饰）长期被谎言左右，在离婚后生活接连遭遇不幸，对周围人的话语难以信任。而在圣诞前夜，雪花静静飘落的夜晚，一家勉强维持营业的小酒馆里，聚集了一群古怪的客人。\n锦户亮饰演光的前夫·小林幸助。竹原饰演不善交际但正义感极强的自称刑警·并木正义。盐野饰演在圣诞前夜盯上独自一人女性的自称婚姻诈骗犯·中村信。", "rating": {"count": 991, "max": 10, "star_count": 3.5, "value": 7.0}, "vendor_count": 0, "has_linewatch": false, "pic": {"large": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m_ratio_poster/public/p2929643459.jpg", "normal": "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2929643459.jpg"}, "honor_infos": [], "uri": "douban://douban.com/tv/37898144", "episodes_info": "", "photos": ["https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2927714860.jpg", "https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2927714859.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929116825.jpg", "https://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/m/public/p2929116824.jpg"], "vendor_icons": [], "interest": null, "year": "2025", "card_subtitle": "2025 / 日本 / 剧情 悬疑 / 菊地凛子 锦户亮", "title": "谎中之谎终为谎", "type": "tv", "id": "37898144", "tags": []}]}